import React from 'react'
import {  Box, FormControl, Stack, Input, Container } from 'native-base'

export default function Home() {
  return <Container w="90%" maxWidth="300px" marginBottom={'250px'} >
      <FormControl>
        <Stack mx="4">
          <FormControl.Label>Value A</FormControl.Label>
          <Input bg='primary.50' borderRadius={'10px'} />
          <FormControl.Label marginTop={'20px'}>Value B</FormControl.Label>
          <Input bg='primary.50' />
        </Stack>
      </FormControl>
    </Container>
}
